---
title: Chilli Jam Glazed Halloumi with Bulgur, Green Pepper and Tomatoes
description: Our Chilli Jam Glazed Halloumi is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220829_R22_W41_UK_F3042-17_MB_Main_2_low-84324ed9.jpg
